data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 1-acre lot, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic allure. Step into a world of timeless elegance with hardwood floors that boast character, complemented by wide baseboards that add a touch of classic charm. The well-appointed kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and sleek granite countertops. The perfect space for the home chef, this kitchen combines style and functionality, making meal preparation a joy.  Enjoy the luxury of two spacious outbuildings that present endless possibilities – whether it's a workshop, studio, or extra storage space, the choice is yours. Fire up the barbecue in your great grilling area! Gather friends and family for delightful meals. Midway, Glenview and TL Hanna Schools. Convenient to Greenville and I-85. This one won't last schedule your Private showing.
